chapters.teach:
```java
static int moyenne(int[] t) {
    int s = 0;
    for (int x : t) { s += x; }
    return s / t.length;
}
```

chapters.starterCode:
public class Main {
    // static int moyenne(...) { ... }
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        int[] t = {12, 18, 12};
        // println moyenne(t)
    }
}

chapters.correction:
public class Main {
    static int moyenne(int[] t) {
        int s = 0;
        for (int x : t) { s += x; }
        return s / t.length;
    }
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        int[] t = {12, 18, 12};
        System.out.println(moyenne(t));
    }
}
